N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 121.4 - Termination of assignment

State Regulations

The Chief Administrator, upon consultation
with and agreement of the presiding justice of the appropriate appellate
division, may terminate at any time any temporary assignment made pursuant to
this Part. Notes
